                            <comment id="13568133" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Thu, 31 Jan 2013 21:36:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The correct config param is &quot;hbase.hstore.bytes.per.checksum&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See Store.java line 245:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.bytesPerChecksum = getBytesPerChecksum(conf);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I couldn&apos;t find the config parameter you cited.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13568144" author="rshroff" created="Thu, 31 Jan 2013 21:43:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its the one added by JIRA 2478, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2478&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2478&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13568148" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Thu, 31 Jan 2013 21:49:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2478&quot; title=&quot;Experiment with alternate settings for io.bytes.per.checksum for HFiles&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2478&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2478&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is still open.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like this JIRA is for 0.89-fb branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13568432" author="anoopsamjohn" created="Fri, 1 Feb 2013 03:38:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yuzhihong%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yuzhihong@gmail.com&quot;&gt;Ted Yu&lt;/a&gt;  You are correct. The config param name is &quot;hbase.hstore.bytes.per.checksum&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rshroff&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rshroff&quot;&gt;Rishit Shroff&lt;/a&gt; Can you try with this?  Which version you are using ? Not 0.94.x?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13568481" author="rshroff" created="Fri, 1 Feb 2013 04:56:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;its for 89-fb branch. I on the 0.89 version.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
